message: Hi Bob, I'm selling this fantastic product. I'm asking for $90 for it.  Let me know what you think!
Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer. I believe I can offer you $85 for the product. It's within my budget and I hope we can come to an agreement.
Bob, I appreciate your counteroffer.  I'm willing to come down a bit to $88.  Let's see if we can make this work.
